"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"流程：\\n\\n1、创建幻象钱包，并备份好助剂词<https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/phantom/bfnaelmomeimhlpmgjnjophhpkkoljpa>\\n\\n2、币安转USDC（或sol）到创建好的钱包\\n\\n3、打开项目网站[https://www.drift.trade/](https://www.drift.trade)\\n\\n连接上钱包后点链接存款存入钱包里的USDC或sol\\n\\n4、在交易页面目录点击SOL-BUY-在Est。入场价格输入要购买的USDC金额，Size选择SOL，杠杆选择50%或75%，Slippage Tolerance0.5%，再点BUY SOL，完成交互。\\n\\n5、在帖子列表里选择里看到过的订单，点击关闭（弹窗100%）\\n\\n6、完成一次BUY交互。7、返回第4步点击SOL-SELL-在Est。入场价格输入要购买的USDC金额，Size选择SOL，杠杆选择50%或75%，Slippage Tolerance0.5%，再点BUY SOL，完成交互。\\n\\n8、SOL币做完后做BTC-ETH-LUNA-AVAX-BNB的交易\\n\\n* \\\\*建议转10USDC进账10刀在幻钱里编SOL做钱。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FAOdRCmlvc7V4-Ko_d8uZ.png?height=696&width=1315)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641274247,\"title\":\"DRIFT空投交互\"},\"digest\":\"JEFU-cMMUe_MnXq07QDQzDonySPojLciME-bxSqk534\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1AD5E637924561f345560D63c546e372996ba2A3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UZs_LJhrdxCdNt9QH25WpadVa9-pXD4kaJVWPy5t3cQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"C1EC8AcsEGTjR7mPL9u0HkSsq84OZgDPGJNuwtngrDA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ghdj6UyTEoF3gSNP2BNAIwK2m4aIk7KpyVcblYQQUuFbCYBrhcRu7ac2BKHyMVxkz_gw-MiiiRj0zf14oIwoRw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5bb304c3f18d7a1739e6c145e1fa5c6691910f15db06f612533a84bbc74284be47c0877f94f58029e28d13da4802ebed17a228733340c59adfb623bf27915a061c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UZs_LJhrdxCdNt9QH25WpadVa9-pXD4kaJVWPy5t3cQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"C1EC8AcsEGTjR7mPL9u0HkSsq84OZgDPGJNuwtngrDA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"JEFU-cMMUe_MnXq07QDQzDonySPojLciME-bxSqk534\"}"